    "Following that, we propose entropy regularization to address the issue of imbalanced label under nonsymmetric label noise in Section IV-C. A.",
    "Limitations of APL with MAEAs discussed in Section III-C, there are four specific passive loss functions remodeled in APL, namely MAE, RCE, NMAE, and NRCE.",
